Package it.polimi.ingsw.client

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BooleanEvent
    the event is sent to the server by the client,with the answer of boolean choice
    ClientAckDisconnectionEvent
    the event first encoded with a xml encoder, is sent to the server by the client,with the info of socket To Disconnect
    ClientEvent
    prototype of ClientEvent.
    ClientHandler
    it is the main thread for communication and starts the other two handlers, that is, the input and output handlers
    ClientHandlerInput
    ClientHandlerInput it's used for reading the input stream of the server
    ClientHandlerOutput
    ClientHandlerInput it's used for send event to server
    ClientSocketManager
    collection of socket and socket port for the client to access them easily
    GameCoordsEvent
    the event is sent to the server by the client,with the information of the coordinates
    GodChoiceEvent
    the event is sent to the server by the client,with the information of the chosen god and the player that chose
    GodListEvent
    the event is sent to the server by the client,with the information of the list of gods chose by partyOwner
    LoginEvent
    the event is sent to the server by the client,with the login payload
    SetupCoordsEvent
    the event is sent to the server by the client,with the information of the coordinates of the two workers who must be positioned on the map
    StartUpEvent
    the event is sent to the server by the client, with the information of who made the communications and the number of players of the game
